<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Hawking&apos;s &quot;A Brief History of Time&quot; is a good place to start; the ideas cover the basics of physical laws and how the universe operates. Hawking state<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Hawking's "A Brief History of Time" is a good place to start; the ideas cover the basics of physical laws and how the universe operates. Hawking states that this book is a follow up to ABHOT, but it can be read by itself (ABHOT recommended though).<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
